{% extends "BFSiteBundle::base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}
  Rules - {{ parent() }}
{% endblock %}


{% block content %}
<section class="background text-center">
	<div class="row">
	  <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-10 col-md-10 col-lg-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-offset-1">
	    <h1 style="color:white;">Rules</h1>
	      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 vcenter">
	        <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Upload your videos</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	              	In order to participate in a challenge, you just have to go to the “Challenges” tab or “Partner Challenges” tab. If you want to understand what is asking for the challenge, you click on “More info”. You will have a video showing you what must be done. Once you understand what is exactly the challenge, you can click on « Participate ».  You will have to indicate us the level you reached. You can post as many videos as you want and your best level will be retained! Once you have uploaded your video, you receive a number of points according to the level reached you indicated.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>
	     </br>
	     </br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Level reached</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	              	BestFootball always value fun, entertainment and mutual trust towards our community. That is why we let you mention the level you reached while you upload the video. Of course, Bestfootball users can report a video when the level reached mentioned does not reflect the reality.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>
	     	</br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Challenges levels</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	              Each challenge has different degree of diffculty, everytime you successfully reach a level within a challenge, you will get a certain amount of point. The higher the level the more points you will get. If your talent allows you to go further than the maximum level set by BestFootball, you will have the privilege to obtain the grade of « Legend » in this particular challenge. 
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>
	        </br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Challenges Ranking</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	             	Several rankings (global, nationally, by gender…) are made. You can measure your level and compare yourself with the best in your city or around the world.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>
	         </br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Grades</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	             	Grades will be given according to your number of points.
					1. Unknown</br>
					2. Promising talent</br>
					3. Rising star</br>
					4. Star status</br>
					5. Legend

					Conditions

					To be considered as a rising star, you will have to achieve at least half of levels on two challenges. To be a rising star, you will have to achieve at least all levels on two challenges hormis le dernier. To be a legend, you will have to achieve at least all levels on two challenges and be a legend in one challenge.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>

	         </br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Invite a BestFootball user for a duel</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	             	With BestFootball, stop endless debate and let’s see who is better between you and your friends. Go on the profile of a BestFootball user, and click on “Duel me”. Then, choose on which challenge you want to defy your friend. Once the two players have accepted the duel, one week is given to them to post their video. None of the videos will be shown until the two have been uploaded. As soon as the two videos are uploaded, they are shown even if the period of one week is not finished yet.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>
	         </br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">Duel Ranking</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	             	In order to take into account ages difference we made the “Duel Ranking” section. The duels allow you to play against people of your level and get points with are counted only on the “Duel Ranking”. With that method, a young 11 years old can then have a better ranking than a 20 years old player.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>

	         </br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">I have great ranking, and so what?</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	             	BestFootball aims to reward the best players. That is why each semester the best players will get prices from BestFootball.
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>
	         </br>
	     	</br>
	         <div class="challengedescription">
	            <div class="challengetitle">
	              <h3 style="color:white;">What are the prices?</h3>
	            </div>
	            <div class="challengecontent">
	              <p style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">
	             	Wait, it is coming soon! So far, your best reward is the proud to be the best! But do not worry, the team is working with many partners and great prices are coming soon!!
	              </p>
	           
	            </div>
	         </div>

	      </div>
	  </div>
	</div>
</section>
{% endblock %}